These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
House: wooden, cottage, art-deco, cape-cod
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, azure, brown, white
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold, aconite, sunflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, parkour, water-polo
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle, fish, dog
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
 2. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
 3. the person who likes azure is on the far left##1
 4. the person who likes blue is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
 9. the owner of the dog is the wooden house##1
10. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
11. the cottage house is in an even position##4
12. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
13. the person who growssunflower is not to the right of the art-deco house##8
14. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
15. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
16. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| House    | cape-cod | cottage     | art-deco     | wooden |
| Color        | azure  | blue | brown      | white      |
| Flower         | sunflower  | marigold    | aconite | lily       |
| Sport       | baseball | cycling   | parkour      | water-polo  |
| Pet   | turtle      | goldfish  | fish   | dog      |

